paragraphs: Hi, I am Abhishek Rout, a Software Developer at Cartrade Tech Limited. I graduated with a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Engineering from D. Y. Patil College of Engineering, Pune.
I am a Web Developer as well as an Artificial Intelligence Enthusiast, currently working on Frontend Development.
I am also a competitive coder (2 Star CodeChef) and a tech-affiliated article writer on Medium & GeeksForGeeks.
Apart from these, I have a keen interest in playing Basketball & PC-Mobile Games, Drawing & Painting, and listening to Music.
